Last year in April I decided to do my very first live recording. I put together a 13 piece regime of Holland’s finest at the legendary @melkwegamsterdam and we cut 12 songs in 6 hours. With the help of @raafnagelkerke and so many others, we pulled off a serious feat. Many more somgs and videos will follow and expect the full record to drop this summer!! Featuring @durandbernarr the LIVE version of BUMP THE MAN is now out! Full video on youtube. Link in bio to streaming platforms. Please share, comment and like! Much thanks to @udopannekeet for the mix, @optx for the video edit, @danielscotchfilms for the videography, and everyone else who participated! #funkband #hornsection #durandbernarr @durandbernarrfanpage #soulmusic #soulmusiclovers #soulmusiclives #towerofpower #funkymusic #melkweg

Philip Lassiter's new live album 'Raw in Amsterdam' is now available for pre-order! The album was recorded live with a 13-piece ensemble with special guests @durandbernarr and @realcandydulfer and is set to drop June 30 on @colorredmusic. This is a very limited edition record and Philip's first live recording ever so order now to guarantee your copy! 

"The idea behind raw in Amsterdam is that it would take my new band based in the Netherlands and do a live video recording to show people what we look and sound like on stage. We recorded 12 songs in only six hours. It’s full of action packed funk jazz and soul featuring a 13 piece band. The album is set to drop June 30. We have already released two singles. 'Purple', which is a tribute to Prince featuring Candy Dulfer and 'Bump The Man' featuring Durand Bernarr. The next single is scheduled to drop in May is a live recording of “Repent” from the Live In Love album. This will feature Durand and Candy together." - @philiplassitermusic

So excited to start this beautiful event, featuring original artists across the NL and beyond. A night of community, music, industry, soul and lot of love. The level will be high and the vibration even higher. Welcome to Philip Lassiter Presents “Soul Church”.

It’s a constant inner battle. Those who know me know that I can be a scrappy cat. But those who know me well also know I have a big heart.  I’m realizing more and more that if I allow anything to break my stride, it’s those around me who suffer, as well as myself. So I’m making a concerted effort to put myself in the right mindset so I can walk in my purpose. And I think the most important characteristic in my purpose is to be an encouragement to others. Recently we lost a great example of this. Aaron spears, an amazing high profile Drummer but more than that, a very bright light to all who knew him. We kept in touch but I didn’t know him well. I must say, I am humbled and radically inspired by all of the heartfelt posts that almost everyone I know are making for this beautiful soul. And I can’t help but think, I’d like to be more like that.  More than my musical contribution, I’d like for people to pay tribute to me one day as a human first. I haven’t lived up to that yet. Thankfully I’ve got some time to work on it.
Finally.  The vinyl are here. Ft @realcandydulfer & @durandbernarr #candydulfer #durandbernarr

Tonight I have the honor of sitting in with my brutha from anutha planet, @durandbernarr at the legendary Paradiso.  I first met him in Hollywood at this super cool jam session called the juice joint. After he absolutely slayed the room, I introduced myself and was blown away by how transparent and kind he was to me. He had no idea I was another creative or someone he might want to collaborate with in the future. He’s just that kind of guy. He’s a REAL ONE so come down tonight and see for yourself. If you’re not in the area make sure you follow him and check out his albums (some featuring me) on Spotify. Excitement isn’t the word I’m in need of. Maybe there ain’t a word. It’s gunna be epic. That’s all I got.

This has to be the closest feeling I’ve had to playing on stage with Prince and the new power generation since I actually did that. @realcandydulfer is the European Queen of funk in my opinion and 1 of the funkiest alto players alive. Thank you for this opportunity Candy. You are one of a kind. Yes, that is my big sis @therealshelbyj  We were in the prince band together and she held us all down like the OG that she is.  I am so grateful and humbled to be featured as an artist next to these two legends. I’m just trying to keep up. Taking my vitamins and getting plenty of sleep. Lol we do it again tonight in Harlem and tomorrow in Enschede. If you miss these shows then you are missing something that doesn’t happen very often. But I have a feeling there will be more. #npg4life
Whoooowheee sho is fun playin these shows with Candy and Shelby. Long like ve the NPG.

I heard somebody say “F the results”. And I’m hear for it. But I am also grateful for everyone who digs what I’m doing with my eccentric, left of center approach. This song Babayaga was streamed the most. It has been a slow burner. I have to give credit to my co-writers @sputacular @mariahmeshae & @brettnolan Also @benburget_206studios mixed this to perfection. My co-producer pal @jordanrippe played it for the legendary @therealdavidpaich from Toto and he asked if he could play keys on it. (As if he needed to ask) Mariah sang her face off and we had some fun with 4 part harmony with @singlikeyaminit @josjesworld Mariah & myself. @mononeon on bass and a whole slew of incredible musicians made this track pure magic. Thank you everyone for listening.
